{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":110,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_wang_shi_chong","speaker_name":"王世充","listener":"char_ou_yang_xi_yi","text":"希夷兄，道长，寇小弟，请到车内说话。","tone":"平静","chapter":206,"line_start":7,"line_end":9},{"speaker":"char_wang_shi_chong","speaker_name":"王世充","listener":null,"text":"我要改变路线。","tone":"平静","chapter":206,"line_start":17,"line_end":17},{"speaker":"char_ke_feng","speaker_name":"可风","listener":"char_wang_shi_chong","text":"那岂不是很多布置都用不上来？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":206,"line_start":19,"line_end":19},{"speaker":"char_wang_shi_chong","speaker_name":"王世充","listener":null,"text":"我忽然记起当年张良于博浪沙遣力士以巨石投掷始皇的马车，假若敌人重施故技，而掷巨石者乃晃公错、尤楚红、独孤峰、王伯当之流，而我则躲在暗格里，实在非常危险。","tone":"认真","chapter":206,"line_start":21,"line_end":23},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"那么我们示敌以弱之计，岂非尽岸东流？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":206,"line_start":25,"line_end":27},{"speaker":"char_ke_feng","speaker_name":"可风","listener":null,"text":"敌人若要以铁锤重石一类施袭，必须要预知我们返回皇城的路线才成。","tone":"平静","chapter":206,"line_start":29,"line_end":30},{"speaker":"char_ou_yang_xi_yi","speaker_name":"欧阳希夷","listener":null,"text":"内奸难防，世充兄的话不无道理，如若世充兄真的出了事，那就不是示敌以弱，而是为敌所乘。","tone":"认真","chapter":206,"line_start":33,"line_end":34},{"speaker":"char_wang_shi_chong","speaker_name":"王世充","listener":null,"text":"我们目标明显，敌人若要行刺，总会有办法的。","tone":"平静","chapter":206,"line_start":37,"line_end":38},{"speaker":"char_wang_shi_chong","speaker_name":"王世充","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"节原你到车里来，我有几句话要吩咐你。","tone":"平静","chapter":206,"line_start":39,"line_end":45},{"speaker":"char_jia_wang_shi_chong","speaker_name":"假王世充","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"我不想死，大爷。","tone":"恐惧","chapter":206,"line_start":59,"line_end":59},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"放心吧！我怎都会护着你的。","tone":"温柔","chapter":206,"line_start":61,"line_end":61},{"speaker":"char_ling_long_jiao","speaker_name":"玲珑娇","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"这条路线妥当吗？敌人可轻易藏身树上进行刺杀。","tone":"担心","chapter":206,"line_start":67,"line_end":69},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":"char_ling_long_jiao","text":"最怕是他们不来。","tone":"豪迈","chapter":206,"line_start":73,"line_end":73},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":"char_ling_long_jiao","text":"龟兹究竟在那里？","tone":"好奇","chapter":206,"line_start":75,"line_end":75},{"speaker":"char_ling_long_jiao","speaker_name":"玲珑娇","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"为甚么想知道？","tone":"疑问","chapter":206,"line_start":77,"line_end":77},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":"char_ling_long_jiao","text":"人杰地灵，龟兹能孕育出天下无双的乐舞和像姑娘那么美丽的女子，定然是一片非常美丽的土地，所以我寇仲才会动心打听。","tone":"调侃","chapter":206,"line_start":79,"line_end":82},{"speaker":"char_ling_long_jiao","speaker_name":"玲珑娇","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"你是真心那么想的吗？","tone":"疑问","chapter":206,"line_start":85,"line_end":86},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":"char_ling_long_jiao","text":"这当然是由衷之言。","tone":"认真","chapter":206,"line_start":93,"line_end":93},{"speaker":"char_ling_long_jiao","speaker_name":"玲珑娇","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"你知道东突厥在那里吗？","tone":"好奇","chapter":206,"line_start":95,"line_end":95},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":"char_ling_long_jiao","text":"是否在长城之北？","tone":"疑问","chapter":206,"line_start":97,"line_end":97},{"speaker":"char_ling_long_jiao","speaker_name":"玲珑娇","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"算你啦！东突厥之西便是西突厥、伊吾、高昌和龟兹。从洛阳去要经武威、张掖、敦煌、鄯善。到了且末后，还要往西北走上两个月，穿过一个大沙漠，就是我族人聚居的草原了。","tone":"欣喜","chapter":206,"line_start":99,"line_end":103},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":"char_ling_long_jiao","text":"原来这么远的。","tone":"惊讶","chapter":206,"line_start":105,"line_end":105},{"speaker":"char_du_gu_feng","speaker_name":"独孤峰","listener":"char_wang_shi_chong","text":"王世充，你今天死定了！","tone":"愤怒","chapter":206,"line_start":115,"line_end":116}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_wang_shi_chong","name":"王世充","alias":[],"identity":"隋末军阀，洛阳守将","facti